  ('dietitian-moex-11348', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於Osteoarthritis與營養的相關性，何者不正確？ 肥胖導致罹患Osteoarthritis的機會增加 Vitamin C可減緩Osteoarthritis疾病的惡化 Vitamin E, beta-carotene等抗氧化物質可防止Osteoarthritis的發生 Vitamin D攝取不足會造成Osteoarthritis的惡化速度加快', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8c35cacfa49d", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
